{
  "id": "RAW_6c09a198",
  "title": "Andrej Karpathy 2025 年度重磅复盘：我们在召唤幽灵！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247500106&idx=1&sn=2a53337a97619136ae8b7ae473e5d79b",
  "date": "2025-12-21 16:49:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cff318c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlG5Hr4qUmS8mSuDgic7mrz0Snt9qNpjuEasCicZI9icRwRatamKgibDD9w3Oq6zHF2MYNo77fMVmZWdKg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两天我把 Karpathy 的《2025 LLM Year in Review》从头读到尾，读完只有一个感觉：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去两年我们一直在用“养动物”的方式理解大模型——等它长脑子、长本能、长常识。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但 2025 这一年，Karpathy 直接把这个比喻掀了桌子：</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\">我们不是在进化动物，我们是在召唤幽灵。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">幽灵这东西最可怕的地方在于：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">它</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不是为了生存</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">而聪明的，它是为了</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">模仿人类文本、刷可验证任务的分、拿到人类的点赞</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">而聪明的。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以它会呈现一种特别诡异的状态——</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">锯齿状智能</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">有些地方，它像个全知的博学家</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">有些地方，它又像个一哄就上当的小学生</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">有些地方，它可能会出现“奶奶Bug”，被人类骗得团团转。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Karpathy 说 2025 有 6 个“范式转移”。我按自己的理解，简单翻译一下</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 40px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d32f2f, transparent);\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">01｜RLVR：不是模型变大了，是“训练方式 + 思考时间”变了</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025 最大的变化，不是“又堆了多少参数”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">而是大家默认的训练流水线里，多了一道关键工序：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Reinforcement Learning from Verifiable Rewards（RLVR）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;——用“可验证奖励”做强化学习。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">说白了就是：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">在数学题、代码题这种“对就是对、错就是错”的环境里，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\">让模型自己刷题、自己试错、自己长策略。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果是两件事同时发生：</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: decimal;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">训练阶段：RLVR 可以跑得更久、性价比更高，甚至吞掉了原本要给预训练的算力</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">推理阶段：如果你愿意让AI多想一会儿，它就真的更强一些</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 40px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d32f2f, transparent);\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">02｜锯齿状智能：Benchmark 在 2025 彻底不可信了</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">当 RLVR 成为主菜后，基准测试会发生一个非常尴尬的变化：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">只要一个 benchmark 可验证，它就会被针对性优化。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Karpathy 甚至直接说：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">2025 他对 benchmarks 的信任度大幅下降——因为“在测试集上训练”已经变成一门艺术了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以今年很多“看起来 AGI了”的瞬间，其实只是：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它们把题库背熟了。</span></strong></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 40px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d32f2f, transparent);\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">03｜Cursor：LLM 应用真正厚的，不是“套壳”，是新的一层架构</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 在 2025 的意义，真的不是“又一个 IDE”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">它更像是把 LLM 应用的“新图层”钉在了地上，让大家看清楚：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">一个像样的 LLM 原生应用，至少要干四件事：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Context engineering（上下文工程）：把该喂的材料喂进去</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">编排调用链：不是一次提示词解决所有，而是一串 DAG</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">GUI：给人类一个舒服的操作界面</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Autonomy slider（自治滑条）：让用户自己决定交多少控制权</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Karpathy 的判断也很现实：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">大模型厂会越来越像“培养通用毕业生”；</span><span leaf=\"\">\n      <br>\n     </span><span leaf=\"\">而应用层负责把他们组织成“能上战场的专业团队”。</span></strong></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 40px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d32f2f, transparent);\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">04｜Claude Code：AI Agent应该“住在你的电脑里”</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一点我特别同意，也特别关键。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code 的形态，像一个信号：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 正在从“你去访问它”变成“它住在你的电脑里”。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且 Karpathy 点了一句非常狠的话：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">他觉得 OpenAI 早期把 agent 放在云端容器里搞，是走反了顺序；</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">在今天这种能力仍然“锯齿”的阶段，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">先把 agent 放进开发者的本地电脑</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，反而更自然。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这才是真正的“幽灵附体”。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">这让我想起了前几天Manus 张涛的一段思考。张涛认为，Agent就像是实习生，应该用“属于它自己的电脑”，而不是跟老板抢电脑用 —— 基于此，才有了Manus现在的形态。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">请参考</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NDk5MTA0MQ==&amp;mid=2652328821&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0e3942ab34c36390ce71c613965c0bea&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"张涛首次回应争议，Manus 为什么没有被替代？｜清华校园行\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">张涛首次回应争议，Manus 为什么没有被替代？｜清华校园行</span></a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">挺有意思，两个截然不同的观点。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">我是融合派。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">我认为，在一些场景中，Agent可以有它自己的电脑；但是，在更多的场景（尤其是我工作的场景中）—— 我完全同意</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Karpathy —— Agent应该用我的电脑。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">这也正是我对Claude Code的用法。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">请参考</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247498933&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=fa72632c3ed7141c0dfd6069f53e2cf0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致｜对话刘小排\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致｜对话刘小排</span></a></span></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 40px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d32f2f, transparent);\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">05｜Vibe Coding：代码开始变得像纸巾，用完就扔</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">“Vibe Coding”今年火到进了词典，但 Karpathy 自己在复盘里也挺坦白：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">他当时只是随口造了个词，没想到会炸成这样。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">它背后其实是一个挺残酷也挺美妙的变化：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">代码的单位成本接近于 0。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">于是你会做以前根本不会做的事：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">为了定位一个 bug，随手 vibe 出一堆一次性脚本；解决了就删掉。</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">不是因为你更爱写代码了，而是因为</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">写代码变得不值钱</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这会直接改变职业定义：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">以后“会写代码”不稀缺，稀缺的是——</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">会把问题讲清楚</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">会拆解目标</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">会验收结果</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">会把一堆幽灵组织成生产力</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 40px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d32f2f, transparent);\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">06｜Nano Banana：聊天框像 DOS，下一代交互要回到“图形界面”</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Karpathy 这段我读得很爽。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">他说我们现在“跟 LLM 聊天”的方式，有点像 80 年代在命令行敲指令：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">对机器友好，对人类并不友好。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">人类真正喜欢的信息形态是：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">图</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">空间</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">布局</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">白板</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">动画</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">App</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以他把 Google 的 Nano Banana 当成一个“早期暗示”：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">LLM 的 GUI 可能会从这里开始长出来。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">更有意思的是：这不是“更强的生图”这么简单。</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">而是</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文字能力 + 图像能力 + 世界知识</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">纠缠在同一个模型里，</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><span leaf=\"\">它才有资格成为“下一代界面”。</span></p>\n   <hr style=\"margin: 40px auto;border: none;height: 2px;background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d32f2f, transparent);\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结尾：系好安全带</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Karpathy 的收尾很克制，也很扎心：</span><span leaf=\"\">\n     <br>\n    </span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM 同时比我们想象中聪明，也比我们想象中更蠢。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">而且我们可能连它 10% 的潜力都还没用上。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以他的建议只有一句：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Strap in. 系好安全带。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">召唤仪式，才刚刚开始。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: rgb(26, 26, 26) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 700;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(211, 47, 47) !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;\">鬼知道，明年我们还能召唤出什么鬼？ 👻</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深入解读了 Andrej Karpathy 对 2025 年 LLM 发展的六大范式转移复盘，核心观点是我们正从“驯化动物”转向“召唤幽灵”，揭示了大模型智能的“锯齿状”本质及未来发展趋势。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深入解读了 Andrej Karpathy 对 2025 年 LLM 发展的六大范式转移复盘，核心观点是我们正从“驯化动物”转向“召唤幽灵”，揭示了大模型智能的“锯齿状”本质及未来发展趋势。",
  "summary": "文章通过解读 Andrej Karpathy 的《2025 LLM Year in Review》，指出 2025 年大模型发展最关键的改变是引入了“可验证奖励强化学习（RLVR）”，这导致了“锯齿状智能”的出现，并让传统 Benchmark 的公信力大幅下降。Cursor 的出现则标志着 LLM 原生应用需要构建新的架构层，如上下文工程、编排调用链、GUI 和自治滑条。同时，AI Agent 将从云端走向本地化，实现“幽灵附体”。代码的成本趋近于零，将重塑开发者的职业定义。最后，Karpathy 预言 LLM 的下一代交互界面将从聊天框转向图形化。整体来看，文章传递出对 LLM 未来发展的审慎乐观与警示，呼吁从业者系好安全带。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
